Metadata: The Urban Mariner USC Sea Grant Newsletter (April 2020-January 2021)
University of Southern California Sea Grant

The Urban Mariner Newsletter is a monthly newsletter covering the latest news from USC Sea Grant. The newsletter includes news on USC Sea Grant supported students (such as Knauss fellows and trainees), the latest news in education, outreach, extension, marine transportation, funded research, opportunities and events, along with other relevant topics from our program and/or partners.
